Protevangelium of James)፤ f. 64va,1– 68vb: A story on constructing churches devoted to Mary (f. 64a, upper margin: ዘሐንይተ፡ ቢታ፡)  (= extract from the Synaxary, on the 21 of Sane); f. 83ra,9-103v (unfinished): Homily of Minas bishop of Aksum on Mary;
f. 83ra, on the upper margin: Kidanä Mehrät

